00:41:39.060 --> 00:41:43.110 align:middle line:84%
so this is a zero
eigenvector of the K0, right?

00:41:43.110 --> 00:41:46.530 align:middle line:84%
So at the partial mu,
partial mu lambda, just

00:41:46.530 --> 00:41:50.120 align:middle line:90%
parameterize this direction.

00:41:50.120 --> 00:41:54.580 align:middle line:84%
But if you restrict to a
section of it, and then

00:41:54.580 --> 00:41:58.000 align:middle line:84%
