to worry away from it.

00:41:58.000 --> 00:42:00.070 align:middle line:84%
And then this
direction just gone,

00:42:00.070 --> 00:42:03.700 align:middle line:84%
so you no longer have that
zero eigenvector anymore.

00:42:03.700 --> 00:42:05.000 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:42:05.000 --> 00:42:05.690 align:middle line:90%
Yes?

00:42:05.690 --> 00:42:08.510 align:middle line:84%
AUDIENCE: Should there be a
