00:42:32.540 --> 00:42:34.030 align:middle line:90%
Good.

00:42:34.030 --> 00:42:35.760 align:middle line:84%
AUDIENCE: Why does
this issue only

00:42:35.760 --> 00:42:37.710 align:middle line:90%
