01:10:06.510 --> 01:10:13.460 align:middle line:84%
So for any such theory, we
know how to compute the vacuum

01:10:13.460 --> 01:10:14.335 align:middle line:90%
correlation function.

01:10:14.335 --> 01:10:17.200 align:middle line:90%


01:10:17.200 --> 01:10:22.420 align:middle line:84%
Then just what we did before
just immediately follows,

01:10:22.420 --> 01:10:34.910 align:middle line:84%
just D phi then x
exponential i S phi, and then

01:10:34.910 --> 01:10:37.820 align:middle line:90%
D phi exponential i S.

01:10:37.820 --> 01:10:41.960 align:middle line:84%
OK, so again, I always use
omega to denote the vacuum

